title: Kas Hartadi
text:
Kas Hartadi (born 6 December 1970) is an Indonesian <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Manager%20%28football%29">manager</a> and former player, that is currently managing <a href="Dewa%20United%20F.C.">Dewa United</a>.
